import React from 'react'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom/client'
import './index.css'
import App from './App.tsx'
import { BrowserRouter as Router } from 'react-router-dom';

ReactDOM.render(
	<Router>
		<App />
	</Router>
	, document.getElementById('root')
);
